data.description: Newly renovated barn home on over 6 acres is quintessential country living just minutes from town. Incredible natural light with modern, artistic detail throughout nearly every room of the home. Large primary bedroom with walk-in closet and wood, track sliding door. Adorable farmhouse style kitchen with new stove and oven and stainless appliances with granite countertops, just across the hall from the walk-in pantry and comfortable dining room. Spacious 30x50 shop with 10x50 lean-to and large loft, seperate room for your home office, 30 amp RV hookups and 50 amp in the shed. Private acreage that resembles a park-like setting is where you want to start your hobby farm.  Garden space with plenty of room to expand. Fully fenced pasture for your animals and newly cleared acreage ready for your dream barn, greenhouse or vineyard. Brand new carpet and HVAC system. If your family is growing and you'd like extra living space, take your vision for this modern farmhouse to the next level with the framed in upper level.
